Be wary of politicians enticing you with gifts to lure you into political gangs, Mt Kenya youth have been warned. Mt Kenya Youth Caucus chairman Linford Mutembei and Warembo na UhuRuto chairperson Wambui Nyutu yesterday said the region has the highest number of political gangs.&ldquo;The campaign mode is here and we have noticed there are political gangs formed to intimidate others for having a different opinion,&rdquo; Mutembei said. They spoke in Kiambu. Wambui said, &ldquo;The ground is hostile for women seeking political positions since there are gangs threatening and intimidating the women.&rdquo; On Monday Interior PS Karanja Kibicho warned that criminal gangs are regrouping ahead of the elections.